Objective: Analyzed Vrinda Store's 2022 sales data to evaluate its marketing strategy and identify opportunities to boost sales in 2023.

Key Contributions & Insights:

Sales Trends: Identified March as the month with the highest sales and orders.
Customer Insights: Women accounted for 64% of purchases, with adult women (30–50 years) placing the highest number of orders (35%).
Regional Performance: Top-performing states were Maharashtra, Karnataka, Uttar Pradesh, Telangana, and Tamil Nadu.
Sales Channels: Amazon (35%), Myntra (23%), and Flipkart (22%) contributed the most to sales.
Order Status: 92% of orders were successfully delivered.

Recommendations for 2023:

Target female customers aged 30–50 with tailored marketing strategies.
Focus on popular product categories like Sets, Kurtis, and Western dresses.
Launch location-specific discounts in top-performing states.
Release new products in March to capitalize on peak sales.
This project demonstrates proficiency in data analysis, generating actionable insights to drive strategic business growth.
